title: thread 'rustc' panicked at 'no entry found for key'

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body:

I tried this code:

I pulled the latest, played some rebase

```rust
./x.py check
```
